name: Frida Punk 010 - Nothing but a number
description: Fun fact: Although born 6 July 1907, Frida claimed that 7 July 1910 was her date of birth. This was not, however,  for any futile reason. 1910 coincided with the Mexican Revolution that lasted a decade. A deeply patriotic Frida marked the date as a politically symbolic one and it wasn't a choice to merely make her appear younger.
